PROJECT 
Create a program that takes your full name as input and prints your name.
Then,changes the first letter of your name to X.

if your name is David Maina,it will become Xavid Maina

#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
  char fullName[20];
  
  printf("Enter your name:");
 
 fgets(fullName ,sizeof(fullName), stdin);
 
 fullName[0] = 'X';
 
 printf("%s",fullName);
  
    return 0;
}

OUTPUT
Enter your name:David Maina
Xavid Maina
